In the Ulam‑spiral the integer \(n\) lies at the lattice point  

\[
(x,y),\qquad L=\max(|x|,|y|),\qquad 
N_{\max}=(2L+1)^2
\]

and the offset from the bottom–right corner \((L,-L)\) is

| side | condition | offset |
|------|-----------|--------|
| bottom | \(y=-L\) | \(L-x\) |
| left | \(x=-L\) | \(2L+(y+L)\) |
| top | \(y= L\) | \(4L+(x+L)\) |
| right | \(x= L,\; y\ne\pm L\) | \(6L+(-y+L)\) |

Then  

\[
n=N_{\max}-\text{offset}.
\]

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### 1.  Locate 2026

\[
\sqrt{2026}\approx 45.06,\qquad (2\cdot 23+1)^2=47^2=2209\ge 2026,
\]
so \(L=23\).

Bottom‑right corner of layer \(23\): \((23,-23)\) has \(n_{\max}=2209\).

For \((23,-22)\),

\[
\text{offset}=6L+(-y+L)=6\cdot 23+(22+23)=138+45=183,
\]
\[
n=2209-183=2026.
\]

Hence \(2026\) sits at \((23,-22)\).

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### 2.  The eight neighbours

Neighbour coordinates of \((23,-22)\):

\[
\begin{array}{c}
(22,-23),\ (22,-22),\ (22,-21),\\
(23,-23),\ (23,-21),\\
(24,-23),\ (24,-22),\ (24,-21)
\end{array}
\]

Compute each number:

| Coord | \(L\) | \(N_{\max}\) | side | offset | value |
|-------|-------|--------------|------|--------|-------|
| (22,-23) | 23 | 2209 | bottom | \(23-22=1\) | \(2209-1=2208\) |
| (22,-22) | 22 | 2025 | bottom | \(22-22=0\) | \(2025\) |
| (22,-21) | 22 | 2025 | right | \(132+(21+22)=175\) | \(2025-175=1850\) |
| (23,-23) | 23 | 2209 | bottom | \(23-23=0\) | \(2209\) |
| (23,-21) | 23 | 2209 | right | \(138+(21+23)=182\) | \(2027\) |
| (24,-23) | 24 | 2401 | right | \(144+(23+24)=191\) | \(2210\) |
| (24,-22) | 24 | 2401 | right | \(144+(22+24)=190\) | \(2211\) |
| (24,-21) | 24 | 2401 | right | \(144+(21+24)=189\) | \(2212\) |

--------------------------------------------------------------------
### 3.  Sum of the neighbours

\[
\begin{aligned}
S &= 2208+2209+2210+2211+2212   \\
  &\quad + 2025+1850+2027        \\
  &= 11\,050 + 5\,902 \\
  &= 16\,952.
\end{aligned}
\]

--------------------------------------------------------------------
\[
\boxed{16952}
\]
